00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:01.910
Now that we've got GigaGal running and

00:00:01.910 --> 00:00:04.650
jumping, she really needs
something to jump on.

00:00:04.650 --> 00:00:07.600
Let's add the eponymous platforms
to this platforming game.

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:10.610
First we'll talk about the mechanics
of how GigaGal will interact with

00:00:10.610 --> 00:00:11.740
the platforms.

00:00:11.740 --> 00:00:15.060
And then we'll add pretty
9-patch platforms to the game.

00:00:15.060 --> 00:00:18.190
Then we'll figure out the details
of how to check when GigaGal should

00:00:18.190 --> 00:00:21.780
land on a platform and
when she should fall back off the side.

00:00:21.780 --> 00:00:24.590
Finally, you'll make your own
platforming challenge course.

00:00:24.590 --> 00:00:25.140
Let's get to it

